   "en": "President Ishikawa here."
  },
  {
   "i": 2,
   "en": "I saw your stage the other"
  },
  {
   "i": 3,
   "en": "day. You added your own"
  },
  {
   "i": 4,
   "en": "arrangement to the original"
  },
  {
   "i": 5,
   "en": "choreography, didn't you?"
  },
  {
   "i": 6,
   "en": "A bit rough, yes, but fresh."
  },
  {
   "i": 7,
   "en": "Above all, I felt potential"
  },
  {
   "i": 8,
   "en": "there."
  },
  {
   "i": 9,
   "en": "The original is a finished"
  },
  {
   "i": 10,
   "en": "work; a clumsy arrangement"
  },
  {
   "i": 11,
   "en": "could well ruin it, but..."
  },
  {
   "i": 12,
   "en": "keep challenging, unafraid"
  },
  {
   "i": 13,
   "en": "of failure."
  },
  {
   "i": 14,
   "en": "I look forward to the day I"
  },
  {
